{"tid":2368412,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"WhatsApp 算唔算跪？","createTime":"2021-01-16T07:10:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T02:53:50.000Z","uid":59920,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"efbb56acf2a851b95f79489c13ccb349866cd134","tid":2368412,"uid":59920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T07:10:14.000Z","msg":"私隱專員歡迎WhatsApp推遲接受新條款期限<br />\n<br />\n通訊軟件WhatsApp宣布推遲用戶必須接受更新私隱條款的期限。私隱專員公署表示，歡迎有關安排，讓用戶有充足時間了解新條款及私隱政策，以及作出考慮。專員呼籲該軟件在這段時間，進一步向受影響用戶提供更多資訊及充分解說，釋除公眾疑慮。用戶原本要在下月8日前接受條款，否則帳戶將會被停用，新期限是5月15日。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f70a9e6c536b1561640b5ac4fceddcb1cd5a6ddd","tid":2368412,"uid":210382,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T07:11:06.000Z","msg":"打個比如，林鄭暫緩逃犯條例"},{"pid":"244980bda44a8c114b6d0e6cc90e94a6eb564a44","tid":2368412,"uid":386601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T07:11:42.000Z","msg":"呃下你地，再多啲時間攞料"},{"pid":"628943d1d8dd43c0ca812118320e2d564f4dd717","tid":2368412,"uid":59920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f70a9e6c536b1561640b5ac4fceddcb1cd5a6ddd","tid":2368412,"uid":210382,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T07:11:06.000Z","msg":"打個比如，林鄭暫緩逃犯條例"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T07:12:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e172c05c99233060f0a4c022b8ce3de06b754ce","tid":2368412,"uid":59920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"244980bda44a8c114b6d0e6cc90e94a6eb564a44","tid":2368412,"uid":386601,"l